Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.77,deefun,,0,0,0,,别说这个  把一切都告诉我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Stop. Just tell me everything.
